sequenceDiagram
    participant SP as Sidepanel
    participant SW as Service Worker
    participant CM as Cache Manager
    participant Gmail as Gmail Tab

    Note over SP,Gmail: Label Selection / Deselection
    SP->>SW: selectionChanged {labelId, scopeTimestamp}
    Note right of SW: labelId set → label hash<br/>labelId null → #all or scoped search
    SW->>Gmail: tabs.update(url)
    SW->>CM: setFilterConfig({labelId, includeChildren, scopeTimestamp})
    CM->>CM: pushResults — queryLabel + getLabelCounts
    CM->>SW: resultCallback(filterResults)
    SW->>SP: filterResults {count, coLabelCounts, counts, partial}
    Note right of SP: coLabelCounts only present when labelId set

    Note over SP,Gmail: Search Tab Close
    SP->>SW: filtersOff
    SW->>Gmail: tabs.update(url) — #inbox

    Note over SP,Gmail: User Navigation
    Gmail->>SW: tabs.onUpdated (hash change)
    SW->>SP: userNavigated (if not extension-initiated)
